Package: fileinfo
Title: Consistent file-listing across file-systems
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Ian", family = "Lyttle", email = "ian.lyttle@schneider-electric.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: We work with our local file-systems, we also work with remote 
  file-systems, like box.com or Azure Datalake, for example. The functions 
  in this package let you create consistent data-frames for listing files 
  in multiple systems.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/ijlyttle/fileinfo
BugReports: https://github.com/ijlyttle/fileinfo/issues
